      "problem": "There are 6 mangoes. 2 are eaten. How many are left?",
      "steps": [
        "Start at 6.",
        "Count back 2: five, four.",
        "4 mangoes are left.",
        "Check: 4 left + 2 eaten = 6. Correct!"
      ],
      "answer": "4",
